choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for this week.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Monday: Grilled chicken with quinoa and steamed vegetables (broccoli, carrots, zucchini) 
Tuesday: Baked salmon with sweet potato fries and a side of mixed greens salad 
Wednesday: Lentil soup with whole grain bread and a side of roasted Brussels sprouts 
Thursday: Turkey chili with brown rice and cornbread (made without dairy) 
Friday: Grilled shrimp skewers with avocado and cucumber salad, quinoa on the side 
Saturday: Vegetarian stir fry with tofu, mixed vegetables, and jasmine rice 
Sunday: Roasted chicken with roasted root vegetables (carrots, parsnips, beets) and a green salad
